CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 13, 2010

[Cite as 05/13/10 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-2079.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-0853. In re Beuke.

In Habeas Corpus. On petition of Michael Francis Beuke for a writ of habeas corpus, Beuke’s application for a stay of execution scheduled for May 13, 2010, respondent’s motion to dismiss, and Beuke’s memorandum in opposition to the motion to dismiss.

Motion to dismiss granted. Motion for stay of execution denied. Cause dismissed.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur-.
